{"tid":1374043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"寧留命同解放軍決戰都唔好比香港黑警拘捕","createTime":"2019-07-27T17:01:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T17:03:03.000Z","uid":286803,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ab10f3aa465203476d33d82031408ca4b4b5bdaa","tid":1374043,"uid":286803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:01:52.000Z","msg":"好多人都叫前線唔好走<br />\n<br />\n呢個帖唔係叫前線走<br />\n<br />\n而係想提醒<br />\n<br />\n比警察拘捕真係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">唔抵</span></strong></span> 比警察拉你估會上國際頭條？<br />\n<br />\n解放軍會唔會出真係唔知<br />\n<br />\n但萬一真係出而前線既人都被拉曬<br />\n<br />\n要同解放軍打 中線既人你估佢地會上？<br />\n<br />\n所以請大家要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">留命 Be water<br />\n留命 Be water <br />\n留命 Be water</span></span><br />\n<br />\n光復香港唔係一兩個月既事<br />\n要幾耐真係無人知<br />\n中央會唔會插手大眾唔知<br />\n但比人拉左人手越嚟越少到時真係無人再救到香港<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">留行青山在 那怕無柴燒</span></span>"},{"pid":"365ef06419dec3ea6c13a15a0f9ecbd0043e7584","tid":1374043,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:03:03.000Z","msg":"拘捕等於死 ？"}]}